<ShaderNodePreset SupportsAdaptiveDegradation="0" LimitInputsToTexture="True" Version="1.2" Description="
This Matchbox shader creates tesla lightning bolts.


Setup:

- Bolts: how much lightning bolts
- Amplitude: noise amplitude
- Width High: width of the bolt
- Width Low: width of the outer glow
	
- Speed: speed of the animation
- Offset: offset the animation in time

- Lock Left: lock the bolts on the left side
- Source Y: change the Y postion for the source
- Target Y: change the Y postion for the target
- Scale: scale the amplitude for the right side

- Brightness: adjust brightness
- Contrast: adjust contrast
- Gamma: adjust gamma
- Tint Colour: tint colour 
- Tint Intensity: how much tint is applied


Demo clip: https://vimeo.com/151690079

Based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/Mds3W7 additionl stuff http://humus.name/index.php?page=3D&ID=35
